      "Control joints every 10 feet",
      "Edges reinforced with rebar"
    ]
  },
  {
    name: "WALKWAYS & STEPS",
    description: "Front walks, side paths, porch pads, concrete steps with non-slip finish.",
    bestFor: "Curb appeal, safe access",
    features: [
      "Broom finish for traction",
      "Properly graded for water runoff",
      "Tied into existing structures",
      "Code-compliant step dimensions"
    ]
  },
  {
    name: "PAD FOOTINGS",
    description: "Isolated footings for beams, columns, posts, decks. Engineered sizes for specific loads.",
    bestFor: "Supporting beams, columns, deck posts",
    features: [
      "Engineered to load requirements",
      "Below frost line (4 feet)",
      "Rebar reinforcement included",
      "Permanent load-bearing solution"
    ]
  },
  {
    name: "SIDEWALK / CURB REPAIR",
    description: "City sidewalk replacement, curb cuts for new driveways.",
    bestFor: "Municipal compliance, driveway access",
    features: [
      "City permit coordination",
      "ADA/accessibility compliance",
      "Proper grade to city standards",
