      "Non-slip texture for safety",
      "Professional appearance",
      "Most cost-effective option",
      "Works in all weather"
    ]
  },
  {
    name: "Smooth Trowel",
    description: "Polished, flat finish. Best for basement floors (especially if installing flooring over top). Requires skilled finishing.",
    bestFor: "Basement floors, pre-flooring",
    priceLevel: "Standard",
    maintenance: "None",
    features: [
      "Ultra-smooth surface",
      "Ideal for laminate/vinyl over top",
